<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <!-- CSS Stylesheet-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <!-- FONT AWESOME for -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-KfkfwYDsLkIlwQp6LFnl8zNdLGxu9YAA1QvwINks4PhcElQSvqcyVLLD9aMhXd13uQjoXtEKNosOWaZqXgel0g==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-F3w7mX95PdgyTmZZMECAngseQB83DfGTowi0iMjiWaeVhAn4FJkqJByhZMI3AhiU" crossorigin="anonymous" />
        <title>BookClub</title>
  </head>


<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100 bg-gray">
      <nav class="d-flex align-items-center fixed-top shadow bg-white nav-bar">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Search Container -->
            <section class="col d-flex align-items-center">
            <!-- BookHub logo -->
            <a href="/user-feed"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-bookmark text-success fs-3rem"></i></a>
            <!-- search bar -->
            <div class="input-group ms-2">
                <div class="input-group-text bg-warning border-warning search-shape search-size">
                <i class="fas fa-search me-2 text-success"></i>
                <input id="searchBar" type="text" 
                class="border-0 bg-warning d-block m-0 fs-p8rem 
                fw-bold text-success input-size" 
                placeholder="Search BookHub"></input>
                <button id="search-btn" class="btn rounded btn-success">Search</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            </section>
            <!-- profile-items -->
            <section class="col d-flex align-items-center justify-content-end">
            <!-- profile-picture -->
            <div class="align-items-center justify-content-center d-none d-sm-flex">
                <img src="/assets/images/nerd-emoji.png" class="profile-picture rounded-circle me-2"
                alt="profile-picture" />
                <h3 class="m-0">{{first_name}} {{last_name}}</h3>
            </div>
            <!-- user-menu -->
            <div class="rounded-circle p-1 bg-gray d-flex 
                align-items-center justify-content-center mx-2 user-dropdown-button"
                type="button" id="secondMenu" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                aria-expanded="false" data-bs-auto-close="outside">
                <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i>
            </div>
            <!-- user-menu dropdown -->
            <ul class="dropdown-menu user-menu border-0 shadow p-3" aria-labelledby="secondMenu">
                <!-- Profile -->
                <li class="dropdown-item p-1 rounded d-flex" type="button">
                <a href="/user-profile"> 
                    <img src="/assets/images/nerd-emoji.png" alt="profile-picture" class="profile-picture rounded-circle me-2"/>
                    <div>
                        <p class="m-0">{{first_name}} {{last_name}}</p>
                        <p class="m-0 text-muted">Your profile</p>
                    </div>
                </a>   
                </li>
                <!-- Friends -->
                <li class="dropdown-item p-1 rounded" type="button">
                <a href="#" class="d-flex align-items-center text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <div class="p-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-group"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                    <p class="m-0">Friends</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                </li>
                <!-- Book Clubs -->
                <li class="dropdown-item p-1 rounded" type="button">
                <a href="/bookclub-page" class="d-flex align-items-center text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <div class="p-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-book"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                    <p class="m-0">Book Clubs</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                </li>
                <!-- Log out -->
                <li class="dropdown-item p-1 rounded" type="button">
                <a id="logout" class="d-flex align-items-center text-decoration-none text-dark">
                    <div class="p-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-from-bracket"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                    <p class="m-0">Log Out</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
    <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid mt-5">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="display-4">Midnight Society</h1>
          <p class="lead">For all readers that are fans of Sci-Fi or Fantasy</p>
          <p class="fonts">Here you can see what we plan on reading for the upcoming month </p> 
        </div>
    </div>
    

    
    <div class="bd-example">
        <div id="photoCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#photoCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#photoCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#photoCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#photoCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            <li data-target="#photoCarousel" data-slide-to="4"></li>


          </ol>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img src="/assets/images/Dune.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Week 1</h5>
                <p>La Casa De Bernarda es un drama que tiene muchos ejemplos de discurso feminista.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img src="/assets/images/WheelofTime.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Week 2</h5>
                <p> El drama es sobre una familia que es controlado y dirigido</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img src="/assets/images/Nameofthewind.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Week 3</h5>
                <p>Get out of here. Who said you could enter? You’ve left dirty footmarks already. (The woman leaves. The Servant goes on cleaning.) Polished floors, cupboards, pedestals, iron bed-frames,</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/assets/images/Thedarktower7.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <h5>Week 4</h5>
                  <p>Grant rest to your servant Antonio María Benavides, and the crown of your sacred glory.</p>
                </div>
              </div>  
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#photoCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#photoCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
    </div>    
    
 </body>    

</html>
